    "    # Get coordinates from mesh\n",
    "    x_e = gparams.x_mesh\n",
    "    y_e = gparams.y_mesh\n",

    "    v_2 = cvals[1]\n",
    "\n",

    "    # The lever arms are set arbitrarily so that the e-field is comprable to that in the literature\n",
